						               													<description>Command the pride of the German Navy in Bismarck Solitaire, an Original Book-wargame by Worthington Publishing. Lead the German ships Bismarck, Prinz Eugen, and U-boat support as they take on the determined Royal Navy with one goal, Sink the Bismarck!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You have 8 missions of varying objectives and difficultly, plus two training cruises. Each mission gives you 3 tries to best the Royal Navy. Some missions require you to find convoys, others expect you to sink a few British warships, while some just hope your ships can survive the sortie.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Bismarck Solitaire is a pen and book wargame.  In the book you get a map and orders.  You roll dice to see events, move your ship, fight battles, and resolve events.  The only thing you must provide is 2 dice, a pen, and a sense of adventure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A turn is this:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Roll 2 dice and cross reference it to a chart to see events.&amp;#10;Resolve the events.&amp;#10;Fight any battles.&amp;#10;Plot your movement on the map.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each mission gives your victory conditions.  Once you obtain your victory conditions the game is over.  Play missions over and over as no two games are the same.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
